<br />
<span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%"><br />
这些文字你也似乎曾经见过，</span>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">但记不清了。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">你不愿再想更多了，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">你听到窗外有野兽的低吼声，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">你开始害怕了，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">一张纸掉在了你的脚上，<br /></span></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你难以置信的望着那张纸，</a></span></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">风打碎了你手上的文字。</a></span></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">纸上传来了声响。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%">纸张的振动似乎是某种你此前从未听过的音乐，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:华文行楷;font-size: 150%"><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1649115&auto=1&height=66" loop="loop"></iframe></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
